          </LEXSubDomains>
          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-12-11 13:05:53" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>wood as a substance used to burn for heat</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>firewood</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>ξύλον in {S:04202303100012} may also be interpreted as a live green tree (see {D:3.4}). If one assumes that the meaning here is ‘firewood,’ then it may be necessary to translate ‘wood which has not had an opportunity to dry out’ or ‘wood which is still green’ or ‘… which is still wet with sap.’</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
          <LEXReferences>
            <LEXReference>04202303100012</LEXReference>
