              <DefinitionShort>(a figurative extension of meaning of {L:ξύλον&lt;SDBG:ξύλον:000000&gt;}[a] ‘wood,’ {D:3.60}) an instrument of execution.</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>cross</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>Outside the NT ξύλον[f] often refers to a gallows, but in the NT contexts speaking of capital punishment, the reference is to the cross on which Jesus was crucified.</Comments>
